\mt2 O
\mt1 Taitus
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Taitus, a Judan gumazim puvat…®. A Krais…®n g…®n ghua, Pol…®n akuragha an Aposel…®n ingangarim gami. Ez…® Pol ti, Taitus Krit…®n Arighat…®zim…®n sios…®n ingangaribar ganasa, an anet…®.
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam…®n faragha zuir akam kamagh…®n m…®gei, Krit…®n gumazamizibar araziba derazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba sios…®n gumazamizir dapanibar otivs…®, me bar arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®. Ez…® Pol g…®n vaghvagh gumazamizibar sure damuasa Taitus m…®gei. Kar gumazir ghuriba ko amizir ghuriba, ko gumazir igiaba ko ingangarir gumazir k…®niba.
\ip Ez…® ak…®nafarim…®n akar abuananaba kamagh…®n m…®gei, Taitas gumazamizibar sure damut…®, me navir vam…®ran ik…®va, arazir aghuibar igharaz darazir amu. Eght…® me akam adaribar amu akaba uariv soghan kogham.
\c 1
\ms1 Taitus Krit…®n Arighat…®zim…®n damuamin ingangarim
\mr (Sapta 1--3)
\p 
\v 1 K…® Pol, k…® God…®n ingangarir gumazim, egha Krais Iesus…®n aposel. God ua bagha m…®sevezir gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itiba, k…® gavgavim me dan…®ngasa, God na amada. Egh men akuraght…® me guiz…®n akam g…®fogh egh God…®n Arazibar g…®n mangam.
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Rom 16:25; Kolosi 1:27; 2 Timoti 1:1; 1:9; 1 Pita 1:20\x*K…® me damut…®, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…®va, egh God me dan…®ngamin zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim m…®zuamam. Fom…®ra fom…®ra nguazir kam otozir puvat…®zir dughiam…®n, an akar d…®k…®r…®zim e ganigha g…®vagha ghaze, a ik…®r…®m…®rir kam e dan…®ngam. A God…®n ifarir puvat…®zim.
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Efesus 1:9-10; 1 Tesalonika 2:4; 1 Timoti 1:1; 1:11; 2:3; 2 Timoti 1:10; Taitus 2:10; 3:4\x*Egha a uab…® inabazir dughiam…®n an m…®g…®r…®g…®am bar azenim gir…®. God en Akurvazir Gumazim, a uab…® na am…®sevegha akar gavgavim na ganigha, uan akam akurir ingangarim na gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Rom 1:7; 2 Korin 8:23; Galesia 2:3; 2 Timoti 1:2; 4:10\x*Taitus, k…® n…® bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri. N…® na ko n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir vam…®ra iti, n…® guizbang…®ra nan otarim…®n m…®n iti. Afeziar Ekiam God ko Krais Iesus, en Akurvazir Gumazim…®n apangkuvim ko navir am…®rizim n…® ko ik…®.
\s1 Taitus, n…® sios…®n gumazamizir dapaniba am…®sefegh
\p 
\v 5 K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, n…® uan ingangarir otevir n…® amua g…®vazir puvat…®ziba ag…®vagh, egh k…® n…® m…®kemez mogh…®n vaghvagh nguibar ekiabar itir siosbar gumazamizir dapaniba am…®s…®v. K…® kamaghsua Krit…®n Arighat…®zim…®n n…® ataki.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 2 Timoti 2:24-26\x*\x - \xo 1:6-9 \xt 1 Timoti 3:2-7\x*Sios…®n gumazamizir dapaniba, me gumazamizir igharazibar damazibar deraghv…®ra ik…®. Sios…®n gumazir dapanim amuir vam…®ra ik…®, egh poroghamir arazim ab…®ghan mark…®. Eght…® men boriba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ik…®va, gumazamizibar damazibar arazir kurabar amuan mark…®. Egh uan afeziaba ko amebabar akaba munasan kogham.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Ofa Gami 10:9; 1 Korin 4:1; Efesus 5:18; 1 Pita 5:2\x*E fo, Krais…®n adarazir garir gumazamizir dapaniba, me God…®n ingangaribar garir gumazamiziba. Kamagh…®n me deraghv…®ra daru, egh gumazamizibar damazim…®n deraghv…®ra ik…®, kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan kogh suam, me ziar ekiam inis…® me gativagh men ganam. Egh me zuam…®ram an…®ngaghan mark…®. Egh d…®par onganir av…®ribar aman mark…®. Egh me tintinibar gumazamizibav soghan mark…®, egh me uari baghv…®ra dag…®ar av…®riba inis…®, n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.
\v 8 Men d…®penim…®n izir gumazamiziba me deraghv…®ra men gan. Egh arazir aghuiba bar dagh ifongegh, navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®ragh. Me arazir aghuibar amuva, God…®n damazim…®n zuezir arazibara g…®nt…®gh. Egh uan ik…®r…®m…®rim derav…®ram an gan.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt 1 Timoti 1:10; 1:15; 2 Timoti 1:13; 2:15; 4:3; Taitus 2:1\x*Egh me gumazamizibar sure damut…®, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim guiz…®n akabar ik…®t…®, da men naviba f…®t…®, me guiz…®n akar kabar g…®n mang…®. Egh me uaghan gumazir guiz…®n akaba batoziba, pamtem…®n me m…®k…®mt…®ma, me suam, a guizbang…®ra m…®gei. Me kamagh…®n damus…®, me guiz…®n akar e men sure gamizim, me an suiragh gavgafigh.
\s1 Krit…®n Arighat…®zim…®n gumazir av…®riba ikia gumazamizir mabar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibagh as…®gh…®s…®si
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Timoti 1:6; 4:7\x*E fo, Krit…®n Arighat…®zim…®n itir darasi, me akar aghuiba munasir gumazamizir av…®riba iti. Me pura akar av…®ribav g…®a, gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zibagh ifari. Gumazamizir kaba men av…®riba, me Judaba, me gumazibar m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghorasa gavgafi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® sios…®n gumazamizir dapaniba am…®sefegh.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Matyu 23:14; Jon 10:12; 1 Timoti 6:5; 2 Timoti 3:6; 1 Pita 5:2\x*Gumazamizir kurar kaba arazir kuram damuva gumazamizibar biziba ko men dag…®aba uari bagh da iniasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me arazir e damuan koghamibar men sure gami. Egha arazir kam…®n me gumazamizir mabar men adarazi sara, men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibagh as…®ghas…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® me m…®kemeght…® me akar katam m…®k…®man mark…®.
\v 12 Fom…®ra, Krit…®n gumazir fofozir mam, anar…®ra kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄúKrit…®n gumaziba, me zurara ifarir gumaziba, me gumazir bar kuraba. Me damasav…®ra n…®ghn…®gha ikia, egha ingangaribar amuan bar am…®ra. Me mati as…®zir atiaba.‚Äù
\v 13-14 \x - \xo 1:13-14 \xt 1 Timoti 4:7; 2 Timoti 4:2-4; Taitus 2:2\x*Akar kam guizbang…®ra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® men araziba ak…®rs…®, akar bar gavgavimra me m…®k…®m, eght…® me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…®va, egh Judabar eghaghanir k…®nir av…®riba baraghan mark…®, egh guiz…®n akam munasir gumaziba m…®geir akar gavgaviba baraghan mark…®.
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Matyu 15:11; Luk 11:39-41; Rom 14:14; 14:20; 14:23; 1 Korin 6:12\x*God…®n damazim…®n zuezir gumazamiziba, me ghaze, dagheba ko biziba uaghan zue, eght…® me da iniam. Ez…® gumazamizir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh amua, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itir puvat…®ziba, men bizitam zueghan kogham. Men n…®ghn…®ziba ko naviba God…®n damazim…®n bar m…®ze. Egha me uan araziba derav…®ra da tuis…®gha arazir aghuibar g…®n mangan aghua.
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Rom 1:28; 2 Timoti 3:5; 3:8; 1 Jon 1:6; 2:4; Jut 1:4\x*Me kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE God g…®fo.‚Äù Ez…® men araziba men akakagha ghaze, me ak…®rim ragha God gasaragha g…®fa. God bar me gifongezir puvat…®. Me God…®n akaba munasir gumazamiziba, egha me bar arazir aghuitam damighan kogham.
\c 2
\s1 Gumazamizir ghuriba bar derav…®ra arazir God ifongezibar g…®n mang…®
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt 1 Timoti 1:10; 6:3; 2 Timoti 1:13; Taitus 1:9\x*Ez…® no, n…® gumazamizibar sure damu suam, me arazir guiz…®n akaba ko zuiba bar dar amu.
\v 2 Egh n…® gumazir ghuribar sure damu suam, me d…®par onganir av…®ribar am…® onganan mark…®. Me arazir aghuibar amut…®, igharaz darazi me m…®k…®m suam, me bar dera. Egh me navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®n. Me God…®n guiz…®n akam derav…®ram a g…®fogh, egh arazir bar igharaz darazigh ifongezim damu, tugh gavgavigh os…®mt…®ziba bar a da ater.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt 1 Timoti 3:11; 1 Pita 3:3-4\x*Egh n…® uaghan amizir ghuribar sure damu suam, me God ifongezir arazim…®n daru. Me akar kurabar igharaz darazi g…®rak…®rang…®n me m…®k…®man mark…®. Me wain…®n d…®par onganibar am…®t…® da me ik…®rar…®ghan kogham. Me arazir aghuibar amus…®, igharaz darazir sure damu.
\v 4 Egh amizir igiabar sure damut…®, me uan paba ko boribagh ifongeghamin arazim damu.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Efesus 5:22; Kolosi 3:18; 1 Timoti 2:11; 6:1; 1 Pita 3:1; 3:5\x*Eght…® amizir igiaba uan navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®n, egh me God…®n damazim…®n bar zuegh ik…®. Egh me arazir bar derav…®ra uan d…®penibar ganamim g…®fogham. Egh igharaz darazir akurvaghamin arazim damu. Egh me vaghvagh uan pabar apengan ik…® me bagh…®v…®ra ik…®. Igharaz darazi akar kurabar God…®n akam…®n m…®k…®man koghs…®, amizir ghuriba amizir igiabar sure damut…®, me navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®n.
\s1 Taitus arazir aghuibar amut…®, gumazir igiaba an g…®n mangam
\p 
\v 6 Kamagh…®ra, n…® uaghan gumazir igiabav k…®m men naviba f…®t…®, me uan navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®nam.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt 1 Timoti 4:12; 1 Pita 5:3\x*Arazir n…® uab…® amiba bar, n…® arazir aghuibara damu, eght…® gumazir igiaba n…®n arazibar gan dar g…®nt…®gham. Egh n…®n ingangarir n…® gumazamizibar sure gamim, n…® me gifaran mark…®, egh n…® d…®bovir akabav k…®m ifaghatan mark…®. N…® zurara guiz…®n akabagh n…®ghn…®gh derav…®ram akam akun.
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt 1 Timoti 6:3; 2 Timoti 3:14; 1 Pita 2:12; 2:15\x*Eght…® en apaniba akar kuratam…®n e damighan kogh…®va, uan n…®ghn…®zir kuram…®n aghums…®ghs…®, kamagh…®n n…® bar derav…®ram akabav k…®mt…®ma, gumaziba akar kuratam…®n apighan kogham.
\s1 Ingangarir gumazamiziba bar deraghv…®ra men garir gumazir dapanibar akabar g…®n mang…®
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Timoti 6:1-2\x*N…® kamagh…®n ingangarir gumazamizibar sure damu, me gumazir men garibar apengan ik…®, egh ingangarir aghuir men garir gumaziba ifueghamibar amu. Egh me akar kurabar men garir gumaziba ikarvaghan mark…®.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Matyu 5:16; Filipai 2:15; Taitus 1:3\x*Egh me, gumazir men garibar biziba ok…®man mark…®. Bizir me amiba bar, men garir gumaziba dar gan…®va egh me akar e kurir kam…®n ziam fam. A God en Akurvazir Gumazim…®n akam. Me akar kam…®n ziam f…®s…®, ingangarir gumaziba bar derav…®ra men garir gumazibar akabar g…®n mang…®va arazir aghuim men akakagh.
\s1 E God…®n Arazim…®n g…®nt…®gh egh Krais…®n Dughiam m…®zuamam
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Jon 1:9; Rom 5:15; 1 Pita 5:12\x*E fo, God…®n apangkuvim azenim gir…®gha g…®vaz…®, gumazamiziba bar an gari. God uan apangkuvir kam…®n en akurvasi.
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Rom 6:19; Efesus 1:4; Kolosi 1:22; 1 Tesalonika 4:7; 1 Jon 2:16\x*God uan apangkuvir kam…®n en sure gamua ghaze, e God aghuazir araziba atagh…®ragh…®va egh nguazir kam…®n arazir ifongeziba atagh…®ragham. Egh uaghan navir ghurim…®n araziba d…®kab…®n…®va egh arazir God ifongezir aghuibar amuasa, en sure gami. Guizbang…®ra e nguazir kam…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n iti, ez…® God uan apangkuvim…®n tuavim…®n a ifongezir arazibar g…®n mangasa, en sure gami.
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt 1 Korin 1:7; Filipai 3:20; Kolosi 3:4; Hibru 9:28; 1 Jon 3:2\x*Dughiar e nguazir kam…®n itim, e bizir e damut…® e bar akueghamim bagha m…®zuai. E Krais Iesus…®n angazangarim ko gavgavir ekiam sara izamin dughiam bagha m…®zuai. A en God…®n Gavgavim ko en Akurvazir Gumazim.
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Ua Me Ini 19:5; God…®n Araziba 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; Onger Akaba 130:8; Esekiel 37:23; Galesia 1:4; 1 Pita 2:9\x*Krais kamagh…®n ifonge, a uam e inigh en arazir kuraba adangasa. Eght…® e bar zuegh an gumazamizibar m…®n ikiam. Egh e arazir aghuibar amus…® bar ifongegham. Bizir kam bagha, a uab…® uan m…®karzim anigha, areme.
