\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Timoti 4:12; 2 Timoti 4:2\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® zurara akar kabara gumazamizibar sure damu. Egh n…® akar kabar g…®n mang…®s…® men naviba f…®. Egh akaba batozir gumazamizibar arazir kuraba ak…®rs…®, me m…®k…®m. N…® akar kaba God…®n gavgavim sara pamtem me m…®k…®m. N…® pura men gant…®, me n…®n aghuagh n…® iriagh…®riaghan mark…®.
\c 3
\s1 E arazir aghuibar amuam
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Rom 13:1-7; Kolosi 1:10; Hibru 13:21; 1 Pita 2:13-14\x*N…® God…®n gumazamizibav k…®m suam, me gavmanba ko atrivibar apengan ik…®, egh me men akabar g…®n mang…®. Egh me zurara ingangarir aghuibar amus…®v…®ra ik…®.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Efesus 4:2; 4:31; Filipai 4:5; Kolosi 3:12; 2 Timoti 2:24-25\x*Egh me akar kuratam g…®rak…®rang…®n gumazamizibav k…®man mark…®. Me zurara n…®m…®ra ik…®va, arazir aghuim…®n gumazamizibar amu. Me guiz…®n uari ab…®rir arazim, gumazamiziba bar men akakagh.
