\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt 1 Korin 6:11; Efesus 2:1-2; 5:8; Kolosi 1:21; 1 Pita 4:3\x*N…® fo, e faragha uaghan n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®, egha e akaba batosi. Satan e gifaraz…®ma, e God…®n tuavim…®n zuir puvat…®. E inivaf…®zir kam ifongezir arazibar g…®nt…®gha nguazir kam…®n arazibar gara dar amuasa naviba d…®kafi. Egha dar ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n iti. E n…®ghn…®zir kuraba ko arazir kurabar igharaz darazigh amuava igharaz darazir biziba bagha naviba isiava arui. Gumazamiziba en apanim gamima, e uaghan men apanibagh ami.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt 1 Timoti 2:3; Taitus 1:3; 2:11\x*Ez…® God, en Akurvazir Gumazim, a bar e gifongegha en apangkuvigha arazir aghuim…®n e gami. Ez…® an arazir kam azenim gir…®z…®,
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Jon 3:3-5; Rom 11:6; Efesus 5:26; 2 Timoti 1:9; 1 Pita 3:21\x*an en akura. A en arazir aghuir e uari amizibagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, egha en akura. Puvat…®. An apangkuvimra, an en akura. An e rue, ez…® tuavir kam…®n a en akura. Dughiar kam…®n a uan Duam e gan…®ngiz…®, an Duam e gamiz…®, e an borir bar igiabar m…®n otifi.
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Joel 2:28; Aposel 2:17-18; 2:33; Rom 5:5\x*Krais Iesus, a Gumazir en Akurvazim, an ingangarim…®n God uan Duam…®n gavgavir av…®riba bar e ginge.
