\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt 1 Timoti 1:4; 2 Timoti 2:14-16; 2:23; Taitus 1:14\x*Egh n…®, gumazamizir Moses Osirizir Arazibar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bagha uari adoziba, n…® da baraghan mark…®. Gumazamizir adarir onganiba ko adoghodoziba bagha bar ifongeziba, ko uan ovavibar ziaba bagha uari adoziba, n…® bar dagh itagh. E fo, akar kaba arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®s…® bar en akuraghan kogham.
