\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Aposel 18:24; 1 Korin 3:5-6; 16:12\x*N…® gavman osirizir arazibagh fozir gumazim Senas, ko Apolos derav…®ram aning…®n gan. Bizir aning inigh mangamiba, n…® dar aning…®n akurvagh. Eght…® aning tuavim…®n daruamin dughiam…®n bizitam…®n oteveghan kogham.
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Matyu 7:19; Efesus 4:28; Filipai 1:11; Kolosi 1:10; Taitus 2:14\x*K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, en gumazamiziba, me biziba bar puvat…®zir gumazamizibar akurvagh, egh pura uan ik…®r…®m…®rim ko dughiaba makunan mark…®. Eght…® me gumazamizir igharazibar akurvaghamin arazim…®n fofozim inigh…®va an suiragh gavgafigh.
